    "For instance, if we had \"Mr. Brown is living in California, and he is working at Amazon.",
    "He would like to buy a brown jacket.",
    "He also would like to visit the Amazon rainforest\"; it can be seen that both \"Brown\" and \"Amazon\" appear in two circumstances.",
    "\"Brown\" appears as the name of a person and as a colour (which is not a named entity).",
    "\"Amazon\" appears as the name of an organisation and the name of a location."
